official_title: To direct the Secretary of Agriculture to convey certain lands to the town of Taos, New Mexico.

summary.text: Directs the Secretary of Agriculture to convey the Old Taos Ranger District Office and Warehouse to the town of Taos, New Mexico. Sets forth the terms and conditions of such conveyance.
